data.text: @DrsMeena Oh no! I hope she’s okay!
@DrsMeena Bless her heart.   Take care Doc. My hopes and prayers for you and your family.
@DrsMeena Yeah, funny that. I haven't had so much as the sniffles in more than 2 years. We are still masking in public. Hope she's ok.
@DrsMeena But most importantly, so glad your little one is negative and recovering with ice cream!
@DrsMeena We also ordered. Haven’t had to be tested through the whole pandemic, but they are a security blanket.
@Docsocksomaha @DrsMeena Plus side: Millard won’t be any different 🤣 (also I hope your little feels better quickly, dr!)
@DrsMeena There is no doubt that we are seeing loads more GI bugs, URIs, and fevers since the masks are off.
@DrsMeena Hope she’s better soon - we had it in our house too (also #covid negative, phew)
@DrsMeena Hope she feels better. We couldn't wait for our free ones so had to buy from Walgreens.
